  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">LGBTI Inclusive Police Training Program in Ukraine</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Programme de formation polici&#xE8;re inclusive LGBTI en Ukraine</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="FR">Le projet a pour but de soutenir la r&#xE9;forme des forces polici&#xE8;res en Ukraine en ciblant la protection des lesbiennes, gais, bisexuels, transgenres et intersexu&#xE9;s (LGBTI) ainsi que leurs droits.  Le activit&#xE9;s du projet comprennent : 1) mettre sur pied un programme de s&#xE9;ances de formation pour les policiers ukrainiens; 2) donner des s&#xE9;ances de formation aux policiers ukrainiens; 3) animer des s&#xE9;ances de formation pour la police nationale dans six villes; 4) publier un manuel de formation; 5) organiser un voyage d&#x2019;&#xE9;tudes &#xE0; Toronto pour les policiers ukrainiens.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to strengthen police reform in Ukraine by targeting the protection of lesbian, gay, bisexual, transsexual, and intersex (LGBTI) persons and their rights.  Project activities include: (1) develop a curriculum of training sessions for Ukrainian police officers; (2) deliver training sessions for Ukrainian police officers; (3) facilitate training sessions for the national police in six cities; (4) publish a training manual; and (5) organise a study tour for Ukrainian police officers to visit Toronto.</narrative>
  </description>
